'''路易斯堡广场'''（Louisburg Square）是[[美国|美国]][[波士顿|波士顿]]的一个私人[[广场|广场]]，向波士顿市纳税，但并不属于波士顿市所有。广场得名于1745年[[路易斯堡战役|路易斯堡战役]]。

广场本身是一个铸铁栏杆环绕的小型草地，北端为[[哥伦布|哥伦布]]雕像，而南端为[[阿里斯提德|阿里斯提德]]雕像<ref name=fodors>{{cite web |url=http://www.fodors.com/world/north-america/usa/massachusetts/boston/review-96346.html |title=Louisburg Square Review |work=Boston Sights |publisher=Fodor's Travel |accessdate=January 5, 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106031847/http://www.fodors.com/world/north-america/usa/massachusetts/boston/review-96346.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

广场周围的希腊复兴住宅反映了19世纪灯塔山上流社会的审美趣味。2014年，这是美国最昂贵的住宅社区之一，2011年售价达 $11,500,000。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zillow.com/homedetails/20-Louisburg-Sq-Boston-MA-02108/59166309_zpid/ |title=20 Louisburg Sq, Boston, MA 02108 |work=Zillow |accessdate=January 5, 2014 |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301041110/https://www.zillow.com/homedetails/20-Louisburg-Sq-Boston-MA-02108/59166309_zpid/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年售价达$11,000,000<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boston.curbed.com/archives/2012/04/another-big-one-3-louisburg-square-trades-for-11m.php |title=$11M for 3 Louisburg Square: Boston's 2nd-Biggest Deal of '12 |author=Tom Acitelli |date=April 17, 2012 |work=Curbed Boston |publisher=Vox Media |accessdate=January 5, 2014 |archive-date=2014-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904203522/http://boston.curbed.com/archives/2012/04/another-big-one-3-louisburg-square-trades-for-11m.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该广场经常见于旅游指南。[[约翰·克里|约翰·克里]]也在此拥有住宅。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boston.com/travel/boston/must_sees_5/ |title=Boston's Modern Must-Sees |work=Boston Visitor's Guide |publisher=Boston Globe |accessdate=January 5, 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106032838/http://www.boston.com/travel/boston/must_sees_5/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

